data.description: Lovely 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom ranch home. Cathedral ceilings and large picture windows show an abundance of natural light and airy interior. Open concept kitchen and dining area with stainless-steel appliances.  From the dining area go into the private backyard.  The main floor master bedroom has a shower en-suite. Two additional bedrooms and a bathroom finish out the main level. The basement is finished with a separate living area, 4th bedroom, and bathroom. Large storage room does the job right with additional shelving for all of your seasonal decor. The list goes on with the convenience of a two-stall attached garage. Underground sprinkler system in the front yard.  Please call for a private showing.
